{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/extras/gif3.gif?t=1739303358\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blessing In The Darkness is a 2D turn based survival dungeon crawler game where every step counts.  <br><br>Crossing dark dungeons teeming with dark and fiendish foes. The fight under death eyes defy the glory of  church and all that still live in the village. You control a brave cleric who accepted this quest. Keeping faith and just go ahead with wisdom! It will lead to the victory of light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/extras/gif1.gif?t=1739303358\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Evil is just an event between life and death.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the middle ages, the black knight domains the kingdom with the army of evil, spreading chaos and darkness to the lands. In this dark place there are few ways to survive and many ways to die.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/extras/zombies.gif?t=1739303358\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Includes:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">2D pixel art visuals with an appropriate soundtrack</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Killer dark dungeons</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">SURVIVAL HORROR elements: Limited resources </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Regular upgrades and items<strong>\u00a0</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Simple controls</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">15 Dungeons to cross</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Bosses</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/extras/inimigo.gif?t=1739303358\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Advices:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Try not to run out of light during dungeons!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game saves at the end of each dungeon of the journey</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1739303358","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/page.bg.jpg?t=1739303358","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/58af4e24fa9dd9302149af65dc7ba3897d5e7bba/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739303358","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/58af4e24fa9dd9302149af65dc7ba3897d5e7bba/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739303358","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/extras/gif3.gif?t=1739303358\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blessing In The Darkness is a 2D turn based survival dungeon crawler game where every step counts.  <br><br>Crossing dark dungeons teeming with dark and fiendish foes. The fight under death eyes defy the glory of  church and all that still live in the village. You control a brave cleric who accepted this quest. Keeping faith and just go ahead with wisdom! It will lead to the victory of light.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3364080/extras/gif1.gif?t=1739303358\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Evil is just an event between life and death.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"